snippet.textDisplay: Where was Jessica’s family? Did she just tell them, “don’t bother coming.. it’s nothing.” Or does she not have family near by? It was crazy to see her all alone, and made me feel sad for her. In the beginning of the show, I wanted her and Barnett to be together and really did not like Amber. Amber was too much attention seeking and showing off and seemed conceited. But knowing that the show will edit the film to make the crew seem certain ways I knew that Amber was the better woman. It’s crazy that Jessica would constantly go after Barnett and make comments like “with me, he would be sophisticated and classy, and with Amber he will be the opposite”, but then when confronted, she acted so innocent. She also WOULDN’T listen when Mark would talk or defend himself. She would get WASTED and act a fool. I was sad to no longer root for her and realize that she was a hot mess who needed some time to work on some things.
